// pom.xml
        <dependency>
            <groupId>org.springframework.boot</groupId>
            <artifactId>spring-boot-starter-security</artifactId>
        </dependency>

In logs, find the below statement and use it in authentication under Postman or etc.
Using generated security password: 54772884-4f79-48b2-820d-0cf79707b41a


Basic authentication can be defined in application.properties.

// application.properties
spring.security.user.name=username
spring.security.user.password=password